### Ownership legend

- **scaffold-once** — created if missing; never overwritten after you edit it.
- **managed** — updated when the template changes **and** the file still matches the last generated hash; conflicts fail closed unless you pass `--force-managed PATH`.
- **derived** — recomputed by the builder; do not hand-edit.

